Package: cgjrapp
Title: Country Growth and Jobs Report Institutional Dashboard
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("World Bank PIDA Data Science Shop", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "pida@worldbank.org")
Description: A Shiny dashboard that visualises Closeness-to-Frontier (CTF)
    governance indicator data from the 'cgjrdata' package. The app supplements
    the institutional chapter of the Country Growth and Jobs Report (CGJR)
    guidance note, enabling country-level benchmarking across four governance
    clusters and thirteen subclusters.
